{"tid":2161823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【毛孟靜留任】對得住抗爭派對你嘅愛護嗎？","createTime":"2020-08-17T18:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T08:35:27.000Z","uid":27986,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f6e1b8c5c36c94d12fa09b483d04b68d92b0df","tid":2161823,"uid":27986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T18:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mDEZ2Or.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmDEZ2Or.png&h=dfb9f5f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與陳、朱同屬議會陣線的<span class=\"red\">毛孟靜表示，個人傾向留下，因為擔心街頭陣線及國際線另外兩條戰線抗爭代價越來越高，起碼留議會這一條戰線</span>，「一班士兵在戰場上不輕言放棄」。<br />\n<br />\n「我仍然覺得議會是一個戰場，不能就此放棄。財委會可以在無人提問下，幾分鐘就過一個撥款，甚至更短，予取予攜。」她如是形容。<span class=\"red\">她又擔心，假設民調正反爭持，同時四成贊成或反對，民主派「真喺瞓喺度」</span>，更可能因拒絕接受民調加深分裂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/32998/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%BB%B6%E4%BB%BB-%E7%B8%BD%E8%BE%AD-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%B4%BE-32998/%E3%80%90%E5%BB%B6%E4%BB%BBvs%E7%B8%BD%E8%BE%AD%E3%80%91%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E5%A4%9A%E7%9B%BC%E7%95%99%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%99%A3%E7%B7%9A-%E9%BB%83%E7%A2%A7%E9%9B%B2%EF%BC%9A%E9%98%BB%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AE%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7-%E9%99%B3%E5%BF%97%E5%85%A8%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90%E6%9C%83%E8%B5%B0%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F32998%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25BE%25AD-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%25B4%25BE-32998%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BB%25BBvs%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25A4%259A%25E7%259B%25BC%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2599%25A3%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E9%259B%25B2%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%2598%25BB%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AE%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2585%25A8%25EF%25BC%259A